{"tid":337630,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人品行係點睇佢揸車就知","createTime":"2017-07-27T12:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T22:13:17.000Z","uid":68842,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de2a75d7a79105ce2a2693aba69d1005295c5ba0","tid":337630,"uid":68842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"如果你有朋友揸車，其實可以睇下佢點揸車 😇<br />\n<br />\n揸車可以睇穿司機本身嘅為人，有啲人係自私無品，就算平時扮得再好一上到路就原形畢露 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由其塞車果陣，總有啲人驚死執輸要緊貼前車，打曬燈遞曬手讓一讓人都洗死咁 🤤<br />\n<br />\n仲有一種就係明明車又唔快但又要死行快線慢線有鬼咁，怕執輸？定迷信？行快線會快啲？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話，之前去日本沖繩，當地人雖然手車比較危險同快之外都叫有廉恥。知道自己慢會阻住人果陣會識行翻慢線，唯獨遇到幾架車行得慢又頂住快線，然後啲人快線慢線快線咁行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望真啲，OTS 租車加外國人貼紙、香港司機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喂香港人，柒出國際啦，果幾個人應該俾人暗中屌左好多獲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f745546561c329f3c1e83458c4dd32862b5d0c58","tid":337630,"uid":31690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"好多人揸車都好自私 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9b0d37ddc8820379f93ef4280842bc9562a37e","tid":337630,"uid":61497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"係日本，車牌見到わ就一定要保持10秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0bae06d4769e3b5575c45f26b3da2013badc5a","tid":337630,"uid":44728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本，車牌見到わ就一定要保持10秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國人貼紙要保持20秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ab4d47cea5f3d50f3d04e6e053906b41512a3","tid":337630,"uid":430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係日本，車牌見到わ就一定要保持10秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd272613cb5c9cb8e15ff6502706e52ef4cc6088","tid":337630,"uid":39668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係日本，車牌見到わ就一定要保持10秒距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n租車"},{"pid":"2f5a7119b3fdabb312fde053fb1e0e0f34ebc298","tid":337630,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76db51dc2f06587d7740855747e0a9b29cdfb9d4","tid":337630,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你有朋友揸車，其實可以睇下佢點揸車 😇<br />\n<br />\n揸車可以睇穿司機本身嘅為人，有啲人係自私無品，就算平時扮得再好一上到路就原形畢露 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由其塞車果陣，總有啲人驚死執輸要緊貼前車，打曬燈遞曬手讓一讓人都洗死咁 🤤<br />\n<br />\n仲有一種就係明明車又唔快但又要死行快線慢線有鬼咁，怕執輸？定迷信？行快線會快啲？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話，之前去日本沖繩，當地人雖然手車比較危險同快之外都叫有廉恥。知道自己慢會阻住人果陣會識行翻慢線，唯獨遇到幾架車行得慢又頂住快線，然後啲人快線慢線快線咁行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望真啲，OTS 租車加外國人貼紙、香港司機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喂香港人，柒出國際啦，果幾個人應該俾人暗中屌左好多獲 <img src=\"/assets/faces